00:00:14.349 --> 00:00:16.533
SY: ...know that we understand our meaning.

00:00:16.734 --> 00:00:18.759
Is a tremendous seeking all over the world,

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:22.096
especially here in North America, so strong.

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:26.342
And of course lots of people are taking advantage of that,

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.680
and exploited it for making money.

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:34.120
The one thing that's obvious is that

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:37.040
none of the previous stages of our evolution

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:39.999
we had to do any effort or pay any money.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:43.273
It's just nature working out its process.

00:00:43.474 --> 00:00:46.193
SM: Is it all right this way?

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:50.446
They can hear Me better like this?

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:54.321
All right?

00:01:18.039 --> 00:01:21.308
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:32.947
The Truth that we are seeking

00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:40.416
has to manifest in our consciousness.

00:01:41.944 --> 00:01:44.888
It is not a mental projection.

00:01:45.791 --> 00:01:48.585
It's not our imagination.

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:54.666
It has to express itself actually

00:01:54.875 --> 00:01:58.107
on our central nervous system.

00:01:58.655 --> 00:02:01.239
That is what the Truth is.

00:02:01.440 --> 00:02:05.039
For example, you come to this room

00:02:05.240 --> 00:02:07.879
and you see these things,

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:11.030
and you see them with your own eyes.

00:02:11.608 --> 00:02:14.189
Through your central nervous system

00:02:14.390 --> 00:02:16.945
you know what it is.

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:23.719
If you feel this is aluminium here,

00:02:23.920 --> 00:02:27.582
you can feel it whether it is cold or hot.

00:02:28.058 --> 00:02:31.359
On your central nervous system,

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:35.983
on your nerves, you have to feel the Truth.

00:02:37.260 --> 00:02:40.829
But we live with mental projections.

00:02:42.566 --> 00:02:45.120
All are mental projections I find.

00:02:45.331 --> 00:02:50.492
We have conceptions about everything

00:02:50.693 --> 00:02:53.959
which can be completely mythical,

00:02:54.160 --> 00:02:56.483
absolutely wrong.

00:02:57.520 --> 00:03:02.393
We have been building them up one by one;

00:03:02.594 --> 00:03:04.422
like that we have built up,

00:03:04.623 --> 00:03:08.606
so many different varieties of conceptions

00:03:08.807 --> 00:03:13.487
and the people who represent one God and one Truth

00:03:13.688 --> 00:03:18.115
are now fighting on the battlefront.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:25.113
It's rather surprising for people to see how they talk of God,

00:03:25.314 --> 00:03:30.560
they talk of love, they talk of all that is universal.

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:33.449
Then why do they fight?

00:03:33.719 --> 00:03:37.659
It's a big question today for your young people.

00:03:37.866 --> 00:03:42.661
And that is the reason why they suddenly become

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:50.000
extremely against God, against His existence.

00:03:50.201 --> 00:03:55.239
They cannot believe that there could be a God

00:03:55.440 --> 00:03:58.879
manufactured by our mental projections

00:03:59.080 --> 00:04:03.597
that has led them to this kind of warfare.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:10.031
That is where we have gone wrong to understand

00:04:10.232 --> 00:04:14.917
that mental projection is not the way to know God.

00:04:17.287 --> 00:04:19.781
For example,

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:27.543
if I start thinking that, "All right, now I am in Houston."

00:04:27.744 --> 00:04:30.759
I am facing people and I'm talking to them.

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:32.738
Do I do that?

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:38.853
I may not be able to even envisage or understand,

00:04:39.054 --> 00:04:41.919
visualize the hall in which I am,

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:43.929
leave alone the people.

00:04:44.130 --> 00:04:47.200
But in My own imagination if I start feeling,

00:04:47.400 --> 00:04:49.439
"This is the Truth, this is the Truth",

00:04:49.640 --> 00:04:51.960
then even the falsehood can become the Truth.

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:53.960
And that is what has happened

00:04:54.161 --> 00:04:57.583
to all those people who talked about God.

00:04:59.114 --> 00:05:01.077
It's all their mental projection

00:05:01.278 --> 00:05:04.076
which has led them to these problems.

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:08.840
Once Mahatma Gandhi was asked by some Christians -

00:05:09.040 --> 00:05:10.840
it can be asked about any religion,

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.960
it's not only the Christians who are doing that,

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:15.614
everyone is doing the same stuff  -

00:05:15.815 --> 00:05:20.096
that, "Why don't you join? Why don't you become a Christian?"

00:05:20.297 --> 00:05:23.735
He said, "All right, but tell me which church?"

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:26.359
And if you then

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:29.553
think about the people who want to unite the churches also,

00:05:29.754 --> 00:05:33.641
what they are uniting is nothing but these mental projections.

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:39.241
And then where do you lie with that mental projection?

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:43.948
So, we have to understand

00:05:44.149 --> 00:05:48.280
that in every scripture it has been said

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:51.839
that you are to be born again.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:54.240
Now, when you say that you are to be born again -

00:05:54.440 --> 00:05:58.038
in 1970 I came to your great country

00:05:58.665 --> 00:06:01.559
and when I told them about this,

00:06:01.760 --> 00:06:08.643
then they started a very big campaign, "We are born-again".

00:06:08.844 --> 00:06:11.276
This is all self-certification.

00:06:11.477 --> 00:06:14.840
What is the difference between a person who is born-again

00:06:15.041 --> 00:06:18.325
and who has, who is not born-again?

00:06:18.526 --> 00:06:22.280
You cannot, just by changing your dress or by changing your name

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:24.452
you can become a born-again.

00:06:24.653 --> 00:06:26.719
Or even a pattern of life

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:30.200
which is based upon only a mental projection if you change

00:06:30.320 --> 00:06:32.827
you are not a born-again person.

00:06:33.028 --> 00:06:35.536
Born-again means -

00:06:35.737 --> 00:06:39.799
in Sanskrit language a bird is called as "dvijaha",

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:42.467
meaning the twice-born.

00:06:42.681 --> 00:06:45.159
Bird is called as "dvijaha"

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:49.325
and a realized soul is also called as "dvijaha",

00:06:49.526 --> 00:06:51.341
means born-again.

00:06:51.542 --> 00:06:55.840
So, a person who is reborn

00:06:56.000 --> 00:07:00.168
has to be a completely a transformed personality -

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:06.003
like an egg becoming the bird.

00:07:06.752 --> 00:07:11.416
What is the similarity between the egg and a bird? Nothing.

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:17.239
That kind of an actual transformation

00:07:17.440 --> 00:07:20.599
is the Truth which one must ask for,

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:27.603
and should not go in for some sort of a plastic transformation,

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:30.516
which is very easy to do -

00:07:30.717 --> 00:07:37.400
you wear one plate around your neck and this, and this.

00:07:38.231 --> 00:07:40.799
Do you become that?

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:44.519
If you say, "I am a Christian", do you become a Christian?

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:47.422
If you go to a church - why I am, say, telling about Christianity?

00:07:47.623 --> 00:07:50.587
Because that's the main religion here,

00:07:50.788 --> 00:07:53.040
but same thing you can about Hindus;

00:07:53.241 --> 00:07:57.117
you can say about every religion just the same.

00:07:57.880 --> 00:08:01.759
So, somebody comes and puts water on your head

00:08:01.960 --> 00:08:05.040
and says, "Now, I have given you the baptism."

00:08:05.241 --> 00:08:08.160
But is that the real baptism?

00:08:08.993 --> 00:08:12.560
What is the living process that has taken place

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:15.604
in a person who is baptized?

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:19.707
We must face it

00:08:19.908 --> 00:08:21.559
and that facing is difficult

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:25.720
because we have built those mental projections

00:08:25.880 --> 00:08:28.280
and we want to live with the mental projections,

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:32.106
and our ego does not allow us to see the point at all.

00:08:32.307 --> 00:08:34.080
But who is the loser?

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:36.801
Not God. It's you.

00:08:37.400 --> 00:08:42.372
You are the loser who want to live and satisfy yourself

00:08:42.573 --> 00:08:45.197
with those mental projections.

00:08:48.595 --> 00:08:52.848
Now, one has to go beyond the mental projection.

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.479
And how do you do?

00:08:55.680 --> 00:08:59.718
How are you triggered out into that space

00:08:59.919 --> 00:09:02.199
where you are beyond thoughts

00:09:02.400 --> 00:09:04.879
and you are completely aware?

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:07.640
Something has to happen within ourselves,

00:09:07.840 --> 00:09:12.026
a living thing, just like a ...

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:17.644
an egg becoming the bird.

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:23.584
In the many rituals that we do

00:09:23.785 --> 00:09:26.728
there's the hand of the Unconscious that guides us.

00:09:26.929 --> 00:09:31.919
For example, on an Easter Day we give an egg.

00:09:32.124 --> 00:09:36.328
I think many people don't know why we give an Easter egg.

00:09:36.529 --> 00:09:38.999
The reason is, that is suggestive,

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:42.400
that you are an egg and you have to become the bird,

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:46.479
because Christ, by His ascent has proved

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:52.503
that you can transform into that subtler dimension.

00:09:53.816 --> 00:09:57.577
But it is an actualization of the whole happening.

00:09:57.778 --> 00:10:01.999
It is not just some sort of a false understanding,

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:05.039
and this is what people don't want to get out of it.

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:09.759
The reason is it's very comfortable to belong to one clan.

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:14.120
Only thing, either it is a Friday for Muslims

00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:16.320
or for Christian the Sunday,

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:18.680
or for Hindus the Tuesday,

00:10:18.840 --> 00:10:21.479
one day at the most you have to get ready,

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:25.109
go to the church, temple or mosque as their case may be,

00:10:25.310 --> 00:10:27.432
and then it is finished.

00:10:27.633 --> 00:10:30.800
You have done all your duty towards your Creator

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:35.154
and that you have listened to some sort of a boring lecture,

00:10:35.355 --> 00:10:37.880
and it's done. That's what it is.

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:40.329
That's what it amounts to be,

00:10:40.530 --> 00:10:42.451
but it is not so.

00:10:42.652 --> 00:10:45.239
Something has to happen within us

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:50.377
when they said that you have to be reborn.

00:10:51.544 --> 00:10:55.051
How much human beings can live with myth?

00:10:55.252 --> 00:10:57.079
Is the limit!

00:10:57.280 --> 00:11:02.159
I mean, the way they live with mythical things and falsehood

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:05.453
is really, cannot be explained.

00:11:05.654 --> 00:11:09.400
The way they go on with it, for ages now,

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:14.239
one generation, two generation, ten generations, twenty generations.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:17.240
They are going on like this with that mythical idea,

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:20.625
and they are becoming worse and worse and worse,

00:11:20.826 --> 00:11:24.623
full of fanaticism which is a disease.

00:11:24.824 --> 00:11:28.213
So now, if you cannot hold your fork properly

00:11:28.414 --> 00:11:30.120
and your knife properly,

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:32.319
you are out of the club.

00:11:32.520 --> 00:11:35.278
It's like that, is that superficial.

00:11:35.479 --> 00:11:38.376
The whole stuff is so superficial.

00:11:38.577 --> 00:11:42.400
So, one has to come to a point to understand

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:45.328
that all this is not God at all.

00:11:45.529 --> 00:11:48.583
It's just talk, talk, talk and talk.

00:11:48.784 --> 00:11:50.960
People will have conferences,

00:11:51.080 --> 00:11:53.639
they'll have big-big seminars,

00:11:53.840 --> 00:11:56.034
and what will come out of it will be

00:11:56.235 --> 00:11:59.822
what are we going to spend for the building fund.

00:12:00.667 --> 00:12:04.461
Supposed to be for God's sake.

00:12:04.828 --> 00:12:06.624
Like yesterday I told you

00:12:06.825 --> 00:12:10.520
that when bishop of Canterbury,

00:12:10.721 --> 00:12:14.520
archbishop of Canterbury, was asked - on a TV it was happening -

00:12:14.721 --> 00:12:16.640
that, "What is Holy Ghost?"

00:12:16.840 --> 00:12:19.239
He said, "I am very agnostic about it".

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:22.731
That means he doesn't believe in God, just imagine.

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:27.308
So, the interviewer asked, "Then how are you there?"

00:12:27.864 --> 00:12:30.685
So he said, "I'm doing my job".

00:12:30.886 --> 00:12:32.786
Then what job is he doing there?

00:12:32.987 --> 00:12:35.855
I saw it with My own eyes, I would not have believed it.

00:12:36.056 --> 00:12:38.159
But what is your job then?

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:43.640
If you do not believe and you cannot explain what is the Holy Ghost,

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:46.199
then how do you bless people?

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:50.179
That, "In the name of the Holy Ghost I want to bless."

00:12:50.513 --> 00:12:53.968
But we accept it, closed-minded we accept it.

00:12:54.169 --> 00:12:58.238
Because they say, "It's, it's, it's a mystery."

00:12:58.440 --> 00:13:00.960
"It's a mystery". But it is not.

00:13:01.080 --> 00:13:02.797
Use your logic a little bit.

00:13:02.998 --> 00:13:06.030
It cannot be a mystery. Use your logic.

00:13:06.231 --> 00:13:08.134
That's how you have missed the point

00:13:08.335 --> 00:13:10.280
that you have not used your logic

00:13:10.400 --> 00:13:12.400
but you have used your rationality

00:13:12.601 --> 00:13:16.869
to build up all these yarns and get entangled into it.

00:13:17.694 --> 00:13:20.719
Now, what is the Holy Ghost? Let's see that.

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:23.119
You have the Father

00:13:23.320 --> 00:13:25.982
and you have the Son.

00:13:26.557 --> 00:13:29.120
And you have the Holy Ghost, but not the Mother.

00:13:29.321 --> 00:13:34.055
Now, can you tell Me of a father getting a son without a mother?

00:13:35.400 --> 00:13:38.192
Simple common sense.

00:13:38.520 --> 00:13:41.879
Absolutely a simple common sense.

00:13:42.080 --> 00:13:45.520
My father who was a very learned man

00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:48.438
and I should say in a way he was My guru

00:13:48.639 --> 00:13:52.120
because he told Me about human beings, how absurd they are

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:56.919
and he explained to Me why they behave like this,

00:13:57.120 --> 00:14:03.322
he told Me that they try to avoid the name of the Mother

00:14:03.523 --> 00:14:08.926
because the Muslims may feel hesitant to join Christianity.

00:14:09.744 --> 00:14:13.651
But Martin Luther himself was a realized soul

00:14:13.852 --> 00:14:17.440
but poor thing, he must have been pressed by everyone,

00:14:17.641 --> 00:14:20.128
"Oh, baba, don't say like this".

00:14:22.041 --> 00:14:26.520
He could not think that it will go on forever.

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:29.016
He thought once Christianity is established,

00:14:29.217 --> 00:14:32.696
people will be able to say about the Mother.

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:36.999
And this is what I am here to tell you

00:14:37.200 --> 00:14:43.072
that it was the manifestation of the Father,

00:14:43.273 --> 00:14:47.732
then of the Son, and then of the Holy Ghost - the Mother.

00:14:48.680 --> 00:14:52.354
Surprisingly, only in India people accept that.

00:14:52.555 --> 00:14:57.358
For them Holy Ghost is nobody else but they call Her as Adi Shakti.

00:14:59.855 --> 00:15:02.280
And any incarnation they talk of,

00:15:02.520 --> 00:15:08.759
first they take the name of the Shakti, the power, the Mother.

00:15:08.960 --> 00:15:11.315
They will not take the name of the Father.

00:15:11.516 --> 00:15:14.658
First the Mother, and then the Father.

00:15:15.589 --> 00:15:18.555
Now, when we talk of the motherhood

00:15:18.756 --> 00:15:22.784
we have to know that it is this motherhood

00:15:22.985 --> 00:15:25.680
which is going to nourish.

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.839
It is this motherhood

00:15:28.040 --> 00:15:30.263
which is going to soothe.

00:15:30.464 --> 00:15:34.282
And this is the motherhood about which Christ has said,

00:15:34.483 --> 00:15:36.273
"I will send you the Holy Ghost".

00:15:36.474 --> 00:15:38.960
He didn't say, "I have finished, nobody is going to come."

00:15:39.161 --> 00:15:42.255
He clearly said, "I will send you the Holy Ghost,

00:15:42.456 --> 00:15:45.209
the Counselor, the Redeemer".

00:15:46.440 --> 00:15:49.996
All these things, He has said it clearly.

00:15:50.197 --> 00:15:53.578
But we do not want to see that.

00:15:53.779 --> 00:15:56.500
We prefer Christ, because He's no more.

00:15:56.701 --> 00:16:01.532
Because when He was there, we preferred Moses.

00:16:04.924 --> 00:16:08.032
And when Moses came, we preferred Abraham

00:16:08.233 --> 00:16:11.080
because it's very easy to handle the situation.

00:16:11.408 --> 00:16:12.590
They are in your pocket.

00:16:12.791 --> 00:16:15.338
Whenever you want you can take it, "Oh, that is Christ!"

00:16:15.539 --> 00:16:17.685
All right, so it's selling in the market very well.

00:16:17.886 --> 00:16:20.382
It's the market issue.

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:24.159
So, when Christ said

00:16:24.360 --> 00:16:27.599
that, "I will send you the Holy Ghost,

00:16:27.800 --> 00:16:32.959
and that Holy Ghost is going to comfort you,

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:35.400
redeem you, and council you",

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:37.920
what about looking forward to that?

00:16:40.920 --> 00:16:42.280
Nobody bothered about it

00:16:42.481 --> 00:16:44.840
because it was too much beyond the ego of people.

00:16:45.041 --> 00:16:47.919
They just don't want to see that point.

00:16:49.793 --> 00:16:51.759
Now, this motherhood

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:57.635
is represented here as the Kundalini, in the triangular bone,

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:00.679
which is the Mother.

00:17:00.880 --> 00:17:05.159
It's called as the Kundalini because "kundala" means

00:17:05.360 --> 00:17:07.679
the coils, it is coiled up.

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:13.452
And this is the Mother within you.

00:17:13.653 --> 00:17:18.199
This is the Mother that is existing within you,

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:21.364
is there all the time, and She is the one

00:17:21.565 --> 00:17:23.839
who is going to give you the re-birth.

00:17:24.040 --> 00:17:29.199
She is the reflection of the primordial Holy Ghost.

00:17:29.400 --> 00:17:32.673
And She is the one who is going to give you

00:17:32.874 --> 00:17:37.814
this second birth which is expected.

00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:41.935
So far it has been as I told you,

00:17:42.136 --> 00:17:45.920
the manifestation of the Father and of the Son.

00:17:46.680 --> 00:17:49.027
And the tree of life

00:17:49.228 --> 00:17:51.963
has grown outside too much.

00:17:53.800 --> 00:17:55.641
The development, the science,

00:17:55.842 --> 00:17:59.800
all these has created what? The monsters of bombs.

00:18:00.368 --> 00:18:02.920
Nobody could stop it.

00:18:04.503 --> 00:18:05.799
Why not?

00:18:06.000 --> 00:18:11.040
Because they could only move on one side - outside.

00:18:11.200 --> 00:18:13.600
They were moving outside

00:18:13.760 --> 00:18:16.247
and they found the big tree grown

00:18:16.448 --> 00:18:18.439
without growing to the source.

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:21.880
And now the time has come for you to go to the source

00:18:22.088 --> 00:18:26.157
and that source is this one, is the Kundalini.

00:18:29.625 --> 00:18:32.439
She is the subtle energy within us

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:35.383
which manifests outside

00:18:36.248 --> 00:18:39.083
the motherly qualities in you.

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:43.839
Now, you may say that the man is the one

00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:47.879
and the women are now having a feminist movement.

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:49.724
That's one of the expressions.

00:18:49.925 --> 00:18:51.959
But the feminist movement

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:54.040
is not what I am talking about.

00:18:54.240 --> 00:18:59.280
Is very mislead, is another kind of a religious, mental projection.

00:19:00.760 --> 00:19:02.360
The feminist movement is

00:19:02.600 --> 00:19:06.239
like a pendulum movement of your consciousness.

00:19:06.440 --> 00:19:09.120
Like, a woman wants to become a man,

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:10.960
man has to become like a woman,

00:19:11.161 --> 00:19:12.279
and the fight going on.

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:14.839
I'm not talking about a rebellion at all.

00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:17.839
I'm talking of a revolution.

00:19:18.040 --> 00:19:21.999
And the revolution has to take place where

00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:26.399
you move spirally higher than what you are,

00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:29.239
not in a pendulum from one to another end.

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:32.719
So this new consciousness of motherhood

00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:34.359
has to manifest.

00:19:34.560 --> 00:19:38.160
And when this new consciousness will manifest

00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:41.800
you will see a man will be changed

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:45.680
into a compassionate, kind,

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:48.919
soothing and nourishing personality.

00:19:49.135 --> 00:19:51.760
It is for woman as well as for man.

00:19:51.880 --> 00:19:57.319
The whole, entire idea of competition, of domination,

00:19:57.520 --> 00:20:00.254
of occupying others territory,

00:20:00.455 --> 00:20:04.800
all these has gone too far of the manly qualities.

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:06.436
They have crossed all the limits.

00:20:06.637 --> 00:20:10.360
Imagine, to come to some country, occupy it,

00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:13.640
throw away all the people, kill them nicely,

00:20:13.800 --> 00:20:16.710
is it a sign of a good person?

00:20:19.287 --> 00:20:22.119
Is it good to do these things to anyone?

00:20:22.320 --> 00:20:24.240
Somebody, somebody comes into your house

00:20:24.441 --> 00:20:27.280
who is a very mighty person with a gun

00:20:27.481 --> 00:20:30.559
and throws you out of your house, and settles down nicely.

00:20:30.760 --> 00:20:33.807
What will you call him? A very nice person?

00:20:34.600 --> 00:20:37.162
All these things have been  so far.

00:20:37.363 --> 00:20:39.119
We have had enough of this.

00:20:39.320 --> 00:20:40.699
Now, what do we want?

00:20:40.900 --> 00:20:43.599
People, who are compassionate.

00:20:43.800 --> 00:20:45.160
Really compassionate,

00:20:45.361 --> 00:20:49.123
not just talking of love and making money out of it.

00:20:50.391 --> 00:20:55.399
But the one who can emit compassion, like Christ did.

00:20:55.600 --> 00:20:56.760
What was Christ?

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:59.204
Did He compete with anyone?

00:20:59.760 --> 00:21:03.692
He was nothing but compassion. It used to just flow from His being.

00:21:03.893 --> 00:21:07.169
A lady touched Him and she got cured.

00:21:08.280 --> 00:21:12.508
Such people we have to create who will emit compassion.

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:16.000
So all these centers as he said - is the Vishuddhi chakra

00:21:16.201 --> 00:21:17.960
which is very important as he said

00:21:18.161 --> 00:21:23.521
is a center represented in the universe -

00:21:23.722 --> 00:21:26.520
your country, America, represents that.

00:21:26.721 --> 00:21:28.960
Is a very important center,

00:21:29.080 --> 00:21:33.239
is a completion, where the human beings raised their heads up,

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:37.009
is a very, very important center.

00:21:37.247 --> 00:21:39.399
But where are they?

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:44.106
I don't think they find that responsibility within themselves.

00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:47.079
Now, what is the responsibility?

00:21:47.280 --> 00:21:51.592
Is that at that center you feel

00:21:53.320 --> 00:22:01.210
that there is nobody who is the other.

00:22:03.720 --> 00:22:07.440
That means you feel the collective consciousness. You actualize it.

00:22:07.600 --> 00:22:10.519
It's not just a lecture, "You are all brothers and sisters."

00:22:10.720 --> 00:22:13.174
It's again mental projection.

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:17.479
We say brothers and sisters. Even husband and wife,

00:22:17.680 --> 00:22:19.359
any relationship,

00:22:19.560 --> 00:22:22.720
it just breaks like that because it is mental projection.

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:25.637
But it becomes actualization within you

00:22:25.764 --> 00:22:30.635
when you become collectively conscious. You become that.

00:22:31.560 --> 00:22:36.742
That means you start feeling others within yourself.

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:43.640
You don't have to think that, "I am trying to do good work

00:22:43.841 --> 00:22:45.640
or missionary work

00:22:45.841 --> 00:22:49.017
and I am going to sort of  build some churches

00:22:49.218 --> 00:22:53.959
or some sort of a place for the poor to come and live."

00:22:54.160 --> 00:22:56.401
Who is the other?

00:22:58.375 --> 00:23:00.719
You are doing for yourself.

00:23:00.920 --> 00:23:03.584
It's just for yourself you are doing.

00:23:04.320 --> 00:23:07.319
If I help this finger of Mine

00:23:07.519 --> 00:23:09.602
am I doing any good to this finger

00:23:09.737 --> 00:23:11.291
or am I obliging this finger?

00:23:11.492 --> 00:23:14.239
Is there any obligation on this finger?

00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:16.359
It's paining, I have to sooth it,

00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:19.093
because it's part and parcel of Me.

00:23:20.202 --> 00:23:22.479
Because it is part and parcel of Me,

00:23:22.680 --> 00:23:26.815
how can it thank Me or how can I feel that I have obliged it?

00:23:27.032 --> 00:23:30.127
How can I have ego about it?

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:34.680
Because it is just My part and parcel.

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:36.600
So what you have to become

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:40.386
is to become part and parcel of the whole.

00:23:40.960 --> 00:23:45.399
As they say, "The microcosm has to become the macrocosm."

00:23:45.600 --> 00:23:48.879
A drop has to become the ocean.

00:23:49.080 --> 00:23:52.400
Has to become, again, I say, the becoming is the important part.

00:23:52.560 --> 00:23:55.352
It's not the lecture. This you must have heard from many people,

00:23:55.553 --> 00:23:58.689
"We all must become saintly". How?

00:23:59.560 --> 00:24:02.879
Ask them. How do we become saintly?

00:24:03.080 --> 00:24:06.959
By putting one red mark here can I become saintly?

00:24:07.160 --> 00:24:09.720
Or by wearing some sort of a dress

00:24:09.921 --> 00:24:12.128
which can be colored in three dollars,

00:24:12.311 --> 00:24:14.422
can I become saintly?

00:24:14.720 --> 00:24:16.199
Let's face it up.

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.840
There must be something happening within us

00:24:19.040 --> 00:24:23.840
that makes us saintly despite ourselves.

00:24:24.160 --> 00:24:26.919
We just become.

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:29.520
So that happening is the thing here

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:32.479
which is called as

00:24:32.680 --> 00:24:35.479
the awakening within us.

00:24:35.680 --> 00:24:39.120
Now this power is the power

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:43.599
of your pure desire,

00:24:43.800 --> 00:24:46.634
true desire, pure desire.

00:24:47.120 --> 00:24:51.359
All other desires are impure,

00:24:51.560 --> 00:24:54.039
because they don't give you satisfaction,

00:24:54.240 --> 00:24:55.879
they don't give you the ultimate.

00:24:56.087 --> 00:24:58.359
Take any desire. Say, you want to have a house.

00:24:58.534 --> 00:24:59.999
All right, have it.

00:25:00.200 --> 00:25:02.366
Then you want to have a car.

00:25:02.676 --> 00:25:03.618
All right, have it.

00:25:03.819 --> 00:25:06.719
Then you want to have an airplane, I don't know how it goes on.

00:25:06.920 --> 00:25:08.840
That's why in economics it is said

00:25:09.040 --> 00:25:11.106
that wants in general are not satiable.

00:25:11.307 --> 00:25:13.416
They are very honest, is... that's fact.

00:25:13.617 --> 00:25:17.839
But there's one want within us which is satiable,

00:25:18.040 --> 00:25:20.258
and that's the true want.

00:25:20.800 --> 00:25:23.920
To become one with the Divine,

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:28.971
to become one with God,

00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:33.160
to enter into the Kingdom of God

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:38.120
is the only true desire within us

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:42.679
and is sleeping in that triangular bone called as sacrum.

00:25:42.880 --> 00:25:46.120
I would like to point out, the word sacrum means sacred,

00:25:46.321 --> 00:25:48.079
that means Greek knew about it.

00:25:48.280 --> 00:25:50.595
This is the Greek word and they called it sacrum.

00:25:50.796 --> 00:25:54.039
Why don't we think why did they call it a sacrum?

00:25:54.240 --> 00:25:56.120
They could have called it by any other name.

00:25:56.280 --> 00:26:02.919
That means it is a sacred power of pure desire

00:26:03.120 --> 00:26:04.560
that resides in it.

00:26:04.761 --> 00:26:06.119
And this is what,

00:26:06.320 --> 00:26:09.960
that is the reason in Sanskrit language it is called as Mooladhara.

00:26:10.160 --> 00:26:11.560
Mooladhara means

00:26:11.760 --> 00:26:16.679
is the support of the root. This is the root.

00:26:16.880 --> 00:26:20.160
And this is the support of the root.

00:26:20.840 --> 00:26:23.359
The center that is below this

00:26:23.560 --> 00:26:26.559
is the center which manifests it,

00:26:26.760 --> 00:26:29.039
is the center of our innocence.

00:26:29.240 --> 00:26:31.080
When we were material beings

00:26:31.280 --> 00:26:35.079
or when till we reached the carbon stage

00:26:35.280 --> 00:26:38.584
we were having only this center within us.

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:46.228
And this center is the center of our innocence.

00:26:46.960 --> 00:26:49.066
And the deity that rules the center

00:26:49.267 --> 00:26:53.880
is the one who embodies innocence within us.

00:26:54.960 --> 00:26:59.542
You can see it very clearly that the center of innocence

00:26:59.743 --> 00:27:02.507
is below the Kundalini.

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:06.999
It is below the Kundalini.

00:27:07.200 --> 00:27:11.476
That means the Kundalini doesn't pierce through this.

00:27:11.677 --> 00:27:15.159
That means this center supports the Kundalini,

00:27:15.360 --> 00:27:18.640
but the Kundalini rises above this center,

00:27:18.840 --> 00:27:23.125
that means sex has nothing to do with your ascent.

00:27:24.160 --> 00:27:28.009
That means you cannot achieve your ascent through sex.

00:27:28.627 --> 00:27:32.864
This kind of a myth has been on and on in the West,

00:27:33.065 --> 00:27:36.199
but in India nobody is going to believe such stories.

00:27:36.400 --> 00:27:39.319
Because they are not so naive.

00:27:39.520 --> 00:27:42.896
Here Mr. Freud - I don't know what to call him,

00:27:44.960 --> 00:27:46.880
you may call him whatever name you like -

00:27:47.081 --> 00:27:49.560
he is responsible for giving you AIDS.

00:27:49.800 --> 00:27:52.415
Please, send him some letters of thanks.

00:27:53.200 --> 00:27:54.759
He is the one who has given you.

00:27:54.960 --> 00:27:58.868
And the way you accepted him, you denied Christ.

00:28:00.880 --> 00:28:06.799
Christ had said, "Thou shall not have adulterous eyes".

00:28:07.000 --> 00:28:09.840
Not only the adulterous behaviour

00:28:10.041 --> 00:28:14.720
but even the eyes should be innocent if you are a Christian.

00:28:15.960 --> 00:28:19.425
Which church has achieved that, I would like to know.

00:28:21.057 --> 00:28:23.255
That is what He asked for

00:28:23.456 --> 00:28:26.719
that, "Thou shall not have adulterous eyes".

00:28:26.920 --> 00:28:30.399
That's only possible when the Kundalini

00:28:30.600 --> 00:28:33.320
passes through that center of Christ and awakens Him,

00:28:33.400 --> 00:28:36.200
your innocence is awakened in your eyes,

00:28:36.360 --> 00:28:39.199
and you really have innocent eyes.

00:28:40.680 --> 00:28:43.157
This is what has to happen.

00:28:43.358 --> 00:28:47.959
But actually whatever has happened you know how far we have gone

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:52.400
with our ideas of licentiousness and permissiveness,

00:28:52.560 --> 00:28:54.960
and our perversion,

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:56.320
thanks to mister Freud

00:28:56.520 --> 00:29:00.283
who was the real guru of the western people to begin with.

00:29:00.760 --> 00:29:03.759
There was only one person who was Jung,

00:29:03.960 --> 00:29:05.999
who was a sensible man.

00:29:06.200 --> 00:29:09.680
He talked of sensible things because he got his Realization,

00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:12.239
but nobody has accepted them much.

00:29:12.440 --> 00:29:16.306
In the whole of England we have only 12 Jungians.

00:29:17.360 --> 00:29:22.159
And the other day I happened to meet about hundred of them

00:29:22.360 --> 00:29:24.559
in New York.

00:29:24.760 --> 00:29:28.477
And I was amazed at their quality of mind,

00:29:28.678 --> 00:29:32.160
the way they understood the whole subject of Kundalini awakening,

00:29:32.361 --> 00:29:34.000
and that the time has come

00:29:34.200 --> 00:29:36.600
for this nourishment to work out within us.

00:29:36.800 --> 00:29:39.694
I was amazed at their brilliance.

00:29:39.895 --> 00:29:44.159
You have to have basically some intelligence to understand,

00:29:44.360 --> 00:29:48.559
and not your ego which just repels you back all the time,

00:29:48.760 --> 00:29:50.200
takes you away from the Truth.

00:29:50.401 --> 00:29:51.960
But have your intelligence,

00:29:52.160 --> 00:29:54.280
your pure intelligence to understand

00:29:54.481 --> 00:29:57.200
that you have not achieved anything so far

00:29:57.401 --> 00:30:00.985
so there has been some mistake, let's see what it is.

00:30:03.112 --> 00:30:07.280
And they did, and they all got realized, you'll be amazed.

00:30:07.481 --> 00:30:11.359
And the president of the organization who was the...

00:30:11.560 --> 00:30:16.340
who was 82 years old, and who is a Jew, got up,

00:30:16.541 --> 00:30:19.560
With such humility he said that, "Mother,

00:30:19.840 --> 00:30:23.619
You know our language of psychology, which is a child science.

00:30:23.820 --> 00:30:27.447
Now we have to learn Your language

00:30:27.648 --> 00:30:30.520
which is the greatest of all."

00:30:30.760 --> 00:30:33.543
Just imagine, for him to get up and say that.

00:30:33.744 --> 00:30:36.635
But hardly you find people of that quality.

00:30:36.836 --> 00:30:40.959
I thank Jung that he created at least hundred people in this country

00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:45.135
who could understand what I am talking about.

00:30:46.981 --> 00:30:52.355
Now, so we have within ourselves this center

00:30:52.556 --> 00:30:55.519
which is responsible for our innocence,

00:30:55.720 --> 00:30:57.960
and when we play about with it too much

00:30:58.160 --> 00:31:00.959
we fall into traps of diseases.

00:31:01.185 --> 00:31:04.491
It is very easy to understand for us

00:31:04.699 --> 00:31:10.368
by our own natural instinct what is wrong and what is right.

00:31:10.569 --> 00:31:13.148
But even if you avoid all your naturalness

00:31:13.349 --> 00:31:17.759
with your all your artificiality and try all artificial methods

00:31:17.960 --> 00:31:19.923
still you'll be amazed

00:31:20.124 --> 00:31:24.238
that those people who lead this kind of life, have always suffered.

00:31:24.439 --> 00:31:29.520
At every port, if you travel, there is a free clinic

00:31:29.720 --> 00:31:32.759
for people who suffer from these dirty diseases.

00:31:32.960 --> 00:31:36.607
It has been there since long, for all the sailors.

00:31:36.808 --> 00:31:38.800
But the sailors don't understand

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:41.280
that we must be doing something very wrong

00:31:41.481 --> 00:31:43.432
to get this kind of a disease.

00:31:43.633 --> 00:31:47.836
Why do we suffer from such a disease? So that

00:31:49.240 --> 00:31:52.239
we have done something wrong

00:31:52.440 --> 00:31:55.040
or something we have gone against the nature.

00:31:55.200 --> 00:31:58.919
When you go against the nature, you get diseases.

00:31:59.127 --> 00:32:02.118
That's a simple thing, is to go against the nature

00:32:02.319 --> 00:32:03.960
is the way you get diseases.

00:32:04.120 --> 00:32:06.600
And you must understand your own nature,

00:32:06.801 --> 00:32:09.306
and integrate with the nature outside -

00:32:09.507 --> 00:32:11.759
you will never get a disease.

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:13.314
And when you get a disease,

00:32:13.515 --> 00:32:17.933
understand that nature is punishing you and teaching you.

00:32:20.160 --> 00:32:28.999
Secondly, this is the biggest achievement in Sahaja Yoga

00:32:29.200 --> 00:32:35.484
that people who have suffered on account of their misdeeds

00:32:35.685 --> 00:32:38.239
very much, in every way

00:32:38.440 --> 00:32:39.999
have been cured.

00:32:40.200 --> 00:32:43.560
Once the Kundalini rises, they get cured completely

00:32:43.760 --> 00:32:45.999
of all these horrible diseases

00:32:46.200 --> 00:32:50.960
which are hidden, which are always kept as secrets.

00:32:51.120 --> 00:32:55.839
They can be easily cured if your Kundalini could be awakened.

00:32:56.040 --> 00:33:00.839
But those who have problems in this center are the most difficult

00:33:01.040 --> 00:33:07.841
because this center is the one which communicates

00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:11.599
everything that happens within us.

00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:15.479
The left-side line that you see here, the blue line,

00:33:15.680 --> 00:33:18.239
is the one that collects all the information,

00:33:18.440 --> 00:33:22.771
called as the Ida Nadi, which manifest outside

00:33:22.972 --> 00:33:25.799
the left sympathetic nervous system.

00:33:26.000 --> 00:33:31.320
And it passes all that information to this center

00:33:31.560 --> 00:33:35.079
and this center passes all the information

00:33:35.280 --> 00:33:40.482
to the Kundalini which is like a tape in a tape recorder

00:33:40.683 --> 00:33:43.079
and tapes all that you have done.

00:33:43.280 --> 00:33:46.440
All the wrong and the good, the imbalances,

00:33:46.680 --> 00:33:51.816
and all the nonsense you have done is recorded in this Kundalini.

00:33:52.764 --> 00:33:56.159
Some people think no end of themselves, I've seen them.

00:33:56.360 --> 00:34:00.239
But when I look at their Kundalini, I feel like crying.

00:34:00.440 --> 00:34:03.917
The poor Kundalini is like a dead personality,

00:34:04.118 --> 00:34:08.559
is like a dead snake trying to rise, trying to raise its head.

00:34:08.760 --> 00:34:11.646
It's impossible for the poor Kundalini to rise

00:34:11.847 --> 00:34:16.960
because you have neglected all that is noble, all that is kindness,

00:34:17.240 --> 00:34:21.520
all that is righteous and auspicious.

00:34:21.720 --> 00:34:24.999
We have forgotten the word sacred at all, completely.

00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:26.800
We have forgotten the word sacred,

00:34:27.000 --> 00:34:30.559
we have forgotten the word that is chastity,

00:34:30.760 --> 00:34:35.468
as if it was something foolish to talk about these things.

00:34:35.706 --> 00:34:39.919
Now, when people start suffering, you start reflecting back.

00:34:40.120 --> 00:34:42.960
Now the new organizations have started I have seen

00:34:43.161 --> 00:34:44.679
with a result of that,

00:34:44.880 --> 00:34:47.200
that they think now you should lead a very chaste life,

00:34:47.401 --> 00:34:48.995
one man, one woman and all that.

00:34:49.196 --> 00:34:51.760
We have in India the same thing - one man, one woman

00:34:51.960 --> 00:34:54.359
but have we solved the problem? We have not.

00:34:54.560 --> 00:34:56.516
That's just a temporary thing

00:34:56.717 --> 00:34:59.879
by which you cannot solve... At the most you may solve one center

00:35:00.080 --> 00:35:02.359
but what about the other six centers?

00:35:02.560 --> 00:35:06.159
What about them? They still exist to be solved.

00:35:06.360 --> 00:35:12.160
And these six centers are very difficult in certain places

00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:16.328
according to the way and style of life you have.

00:35:16.844 --> 00:35:19.759
Now the second center that we have, actually,

00:35:19.960 --> 00:35:22.760
is the center that comes out of the third center,

00:35:22.920 --> 00:35:25.759
so you can change it, the number, doesn't matter.

00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:28.715
This center is the center of our creativity

00:35:28.920 --> 00:35:31.969
by which we go into action.

