Take drugs. Imagine,

00:42:46.678 --> 00:42:50.496
to compensate for this madness, take to another madness.

00:42:51.040 --> 00:42:53.159
Like one boy came to see Me

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:55.109
and he was all smelling, you see,

00:42:55.320 --> 00:42:57.159
had all lices in the head,

00:42:57.360 --> 00:42:58.852
with hair like that,

00:42:59.053 --> 00:43:02.359
son of a very rich man, I knew about.

00:43:02.560 --> 00:43:05.665
Horrible, you see, could not make him sit in the drawing room,

00:43:05.866 --> 00:43:08.879
[as he was] smelling like a dirty pig, I tell you.

00:43:09.080 --> 00:43:10.680
And I asked him, "My child",

00:43:10.881 --> 00:43:13.080
- because I knew the father very well, a very well-off man,

00:43:13.281 --> 00:43:15.376
he's a managing director of a very big shipping company.

00:43:15.577 --> 00:43:18.039
I said, "Why are you like this? What is the matter with you?

00:43:18.240 --> 00:43:20.080
Why can't you be normal?"

00:43:20.281 --> 00:43:23.639
He said, "I am trying to become primitive".

00:43:23.840 --> 00:43:25.199
I said, "Why?"

00:43:25.400 --> 00:43:27.199
"Because they are simple people".

00:43:27.400 --> 00:43:30.079
But I said, "Your brain is not simple.

00:43:30.280 --> 00:43:32.894
It is a modern brain. By growing hair like that

00:43:33.095 --> 00:43:36.319
and putting lices in your head, you don't become primitive.

00:43:36.520 --> 00:43:38.999
It is absolutely outside.

00:43:39.200 --> 00:43:42.800
This is not the way you are going to be a simple person

00:43:43.000 --> 00:43:47.560
by - you see, he was wearing pants with cuts in that and all that.

00:43:47.840 --> 00:43:51.000
I said, "By this, how are you going to cut your brain

00:43:51.120 --> 00:43:53.706
which is so modern, which is so complicated,

00:43:53.907 --> 00:43:56.119
which is thinking all the time about the future.

00:43:56.320 --> 00:43:58.248
This is all outside, don't you see this?

00:43:58.449 --> 00:43:59.960
And you have become so horrid

00:44:00.160 --> 00:44:03.501
that you cannot meet normal people at all".

00:44:03.702 --> 00:44:05.903
So I made him going to the bathroom, have a bath,

00:44:06.104 --> 00:44:08.202
I gave him a change and made him a proper person,

00:44:08.403 --> 00:44:10.000
and then I gave him Realization.

00:44:10.160 --> 00:44:11.840
Now he is a normal person,

00:44:11.960 --> 00:44:13.760
given up all his drugs, everything.

00:44:13.840 --> 00:44:15.960
He is a normal man, behaving all right.

00:44:16.160 --> 00:44:18.978
But sometimes they come in a coma.

00:44:19.194 --> 00:44:22.369
And still with that mental projection that they have become primitive

00:44:22.570 --> 00:44:26.186
they said, "We are very happy. Let us die like this."

00:44:27.560 --> 00:44:31.240
They are waiting for their doomsday. Most of them tell us,

00:44:31.360 --> 00:44:34.189
"Oh, the doom has to come in any case.

00:44:35.120 --> 00:44:36.960
That will solve all our problems."

00:44:37.161 --> 00:44:40.320
Look at this. From this to that madness. I cannot understand.

00:44:40.560 --> 00:44:44.640
Is a very common thing these days that, "The doomsday has to come

00:44:44.840 --> 00:44:46.520
and we are all going to be solved."

00:44:46.721 --> 00:44:48.840
You see, they are all going to be taken up like this

00:44:49.000 --> 00:44:53.469
and put in the God's Kingdom because they have become primitive.

00:44:53.683 --> 00:44:54.879
This is the idea.

00:44:55.080 --> 00:44:57.920
There are some who believe that if they are preaching,

00:44:58.160 --> 00:45:01.399
if they are talking big about God, they will be there.

00:45:01.600 --> 00:45:04.719
Christ has said very clearly,

00:45:04.920 --> 00:45:09.883
"You will be calling Me, 'Christ, Christ!' and I will not know you".

00:45:10.320 --> 00:45:13.999
Do we think about it? Why did He say so?

00:45:14.200 --> 00:45:16.080
So, don't live in a mythical world.

00:45:16.240 --> 00:45:18.759
Come to reality and face it,

00:45:18.960 --> 00:45:21.159
that you are to be born again,

00:45:21.360 --> 00:45:23.720
that Kundalini has to be awakened,

00:45:23.880 --> 00:45:26.280
and that you have to feel the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost

00:45:26.520 --> 00:45:29.560
out of your head and out of your hands.

00:45:30.617 --> 00:45:33.205
This is the first time you feel the All-Pervading Power

00:45:33.406 --> 00:45:35.679
as I told you yesterday.

