Now I met all kinds.

00:45:37.960 --> 00:45:42.282
So, there is one fellow very ego-oriented, came to Me.

00:45:42.483 --> 00:45:44.440
He got Realization luckily somehow,

00:45:44.641 --> 00:45:47.120
his ego, the balloon, went down and he got Realization.

00:45:47.321 --> 00:45:49.620
I was amazed. How?

00:45:49.821 --> 00:45:52.200
The Divine is so anxious to give Realization

00:45:52.401 --> 00:45:54.538
that this fellow came with such a big balloon

00:45:54.739 --> 00:45:57.803
and how it has reduced. It reduced really I must say.

00:45:58.004 --> 00:46:01.236
He got Realization. But then it came back again.

00:46:01.437 --> 00:46:04.759
Because it was just there for a while, again it came back.

00:46:04.960 --> 00:46:07.788
So he says, "Mother, why You are the one who has to do it?"

00:46:07.989 --> 00:46:11.280
I said, "My son, you do it. I'll be very happy.

00:46:11.520 --> 00:46:13.378
Should I change My seat with you?

00:46:13.579 --> 00:46:16.179
I'll be very happy if you come and do it yourself.

00:46:16.380 --> 00:46:19.471
That's the best thing that you can do to Me is to do the job.

00:46:19.672 --> 00:46:21.826
But only thing, you will have to awaken

00:46:22.027 --> 00:46:25.280
the Kundalini of thousands of people at a time

00:46:25.481 --> 00:46:28.319
which is like a mountain being lifted with a finger.

00:46:28.520 --> 00:46:30.239
That's one only thing you have to do.

00:46:30.440 --> 00:46:33.080
Secondly, you have to know all about it

00:46:33.280 --> 00:46:35.280
and you have to tell people what it is,

00:46:35.481 --> 00:46:38.159
all the complications, all the decoding and everything

00:46:38.360 --> 00:46:40.800
and you have to have tremendous patience

00:46:40.960 --> 00:46:45.119
with people who have this big balloon on their heads."

00:46:45.320 --> 00:46:47.996
So then he sat down, he wouldn't accept it.

00:46:48.197 --> 00:46:50.799
I said, "What I get out of it?

00:46:51.000 --> 00:46:53.880
Why do you feel so hurt if it is Me?

00:46:54.040 --> 00:46:56.241
I don't know, really, even to handle a camera,

00:46:56.442 --> 00:46:58.357
I don't know so many things that you know.

00:46:58.558 --> 00:47:00.759
I don't  know how to drive. I never feel hurt.

00:47:00.960 --> 00:47:03.599
I know only one little thing is how to raise Kundalini.

00:47:03.800 --> 00:47:07.083
Why should you be so much hurt about it?"

00:47:08.000 --> 00:47:11.239
This is the thing that crucified Christ.

00:47:11.440 --> 00:47:13.199
The ego.

00:47:13.400 --> 00:47:15.960
They crucified, not only crucified Him,

00:47:16.160 --> 00:47:18.698
they gave poisons and they tortured.

00:47:18.899 --> 00:47:21.878
Anybody who came with the Truth had to be tortured

00:47:22.079 --> 00:47:25.998
because everybody had such an ego and a collective ego.

00:47:27.573 --> 00:47:30.280
Why blame the Romans and why Romans blamed them?

00:47:30.520 --> 00:47:34.039
Even today I find so many sitting like that before Me.

00:47:34.240 --> 00:47:38.172
The same style of people who have crucified Christ.

00:47:39.144 --> 00:47:42.555
So, this is the kind of people who are very ego-oriented,

00:47:42.756 --> 00:47:44.880
and when this center works fast

00:47:45.081 --> 00:47:48.929
the ego starts rising like a by-product as you see in the head,

00:47:49.130 --> 00:47:52.194
that yellow stuff which is horrid.

00:47:53.872 --> 00:47:56.879
But when you start seeing it, you see the joke

00:47:57.080 --> 00:48:00.479
that "This is the one which makes us stupid,

00:48:00.680 --> 00:48:04.239
this is the thing which has really made us idiotic,

00:48:04.440 --> 00:48:06.599
otherwise we will be normal people".

00:48:06.800 --> 00:48:08.453
And then you want to ran away.

00:48:08.654 --> 00:48:11.799
Like one gentleman came to Me, said, "Mother,

00:48:12.000 --> 00:48:15.000
I just want to know one thing, but if it is true, don't tell me."

00:48:15.201 --> 00:48:17.366
I said, "What is it?"

00:48:18.171 --> 00:48:19.573
I said, "What's the problem?"

00:48:19.774 --> 00:48:22.960
He said, "Please, tell me if I was Napoleon in last life".

00:48:23.177 --> 00:48:26.399
"If I was, don't tell me, because I'll really collapse".

00:48:26.600 --> 00:48:27.879
He is, he is a Frenchman.

00:48:28.080 --> 00:48:32.319
So, I said: "Why, what makes you think that you were Napoleon?"

00:48:32.520 --> 00:48:34.445
"Because I am so ego-oriented,

00:48:34.646 --> 00:48:38.159
and I can draw very well which he used to do.

00:48:38.360 --> 00:48:40.240
So, was I Napoleon?"

00:48:40.441 --> 00:48:43.959
I said, "Should I tell you? You were not". "Thank God", he said.

00:48:44.160 --> 00:48:46.439
"Because I was thinking if I was Napoleon

00:48:46.640 --> 00:48:50.079
what will I do in Sahaja Yoga? I just cannot become spontaneous

00:48:50.280 --> 00:48:53.600
because this ego will be coming like Napoleon's ego every time".

00:48:53.801 --> 00:48:55.800
And it's - nowadays once upon a time

00:48:56.001 --> 00:48:58.080
Napoleon who was supposed to be a hero

00:48:58.280 --> 00:49:00.920
today is regarded as a curse on people.

00:49:01.121 --> 00:49:04.155
If you call somebody Napoleon, never call a Frenchman

00:49:04.356 --> 00:49:06.859
because you'll have a black eye, I can tell you this much.

00:49:07.060 --> 00:49:10.119
Napoleon is the worst word for them. They don't like it.

00:49:10.320 --> 00:49:13.831
So this is what has come out of all this ego-behaviour

00:49:14.040 --> 00:49:15.293
that people don't like it.

