What about Hitler? You talk about Hitler to a German,

00:49:18.255 --> 00:49:21.319
he says, "Don't talk, that was a big mistake on our part."

00:49:21.520 --> 00:49:25.008
What did Hitler do? The same thing, he pampered the ego of people,

00:49:25.209 --> 00:49:28.319
he said, "You are a special race with a special nose."

00:49:28.520 --> 00:49:30.441
So, God is going to measure your nose

00:49:30.642 --> 00:49:32.559
and put you on a higher pedestal.

00:49:32.760 --> 00:49:34.199
Just imagine.

