Then why did God create all the rest of them?

00:49:37.960 --> 00:49:40.190
This kind of mental projection

00:49:40.391 --> 00:49:42.439
makes you feel higher,

00:49:42.640 --> 00:49:44.399
sometimes lower,

00:49:44.600 --> 00:49:47.160
all kinds of these mythical things are there.

