I also could not speak with that because you are all within Me

01:18:07.616 --> 01:18:09.824
and this was all caught up. I didn't know what to say

01:18:10.025 --> 01:18:11.744
but thank God it's released a little bit.

01:18:11.960 --> 01:18:16.011
Don't feel guilty about anything, first of all.

