So, put this left side towards Me.

01:18:59.080 --> 01:19:01.287
Not of pure desire,

01:19:02.120 --> 01:19:03.919
but of your desires.

01:19:04.120 --> 01:19:06.879
So, put the left hand towards Me like this,

01:19:07.080 --> 01:19:08.804
and the right hand also like this,

01:19:09.005 --> 01:19:12.040
and I will tell you how to use the right side;

01:19:12.280 --> 01:19:15.564
because the right side is the power of your action.

01:19:15.765 --> 01:19:17.319
Please, sit down, all of you

01:19:17.520 --> 01:19:21.359
with your both the feet on the Mother Earth, properly,

01:19:21.560 --> 01:19:26.572
with a little humble attitude towards it.

01:19:39.040 --> 01:19:41.187
Now,

01:19:42.200 --> 01:19:44.925
you have to close your eyes,

