01:19:53.720 --> 01:19:55.880
because something has to happen within,

01:19:56.081 --> 01:19:57.999
so keep your eyes shut.

01:19:58.200 --> 01:20:01.950
Comfortably, just keep your eyes shut.

01:20:07.440 --> 01:20:09.960
Now, please, do the things I tell you,

01:20:10.161 --> 01:20:12.599
just put your left hand towards Me,

01:20:12.800 --> 01:20:17.479
and the right hand is now to be lifted to your heart.

01:20:17.680 --> 01:20:20.239
On the left-hand side is your heart.

01:20:20.440 --> 01:20:24.542
Put your right hand on your heart.

