You have to sit straight

01:20:33.840 --> 01:20:38.762
with your neck straight, not bending forward or backward.

01:20:45.200 --> 01:20:48.601
With a cheerful mood you have to sit down,

01:20:48.802 --> 01:20:50.720
and not with a laughing or a smiling one

01:20:50.921 --> 01:20:52.839
but a cheerfulness inside.

01:20:53.040 --> 01:20:55.965
Not with unhappy mood either.

01:20:58.511 --> 01:21:03.607
Because this is you are going to achieve which

01:21:05.400 --> 01:21:09.599
has been your longing for ages now, and you are going to get it.

01:21:09.800 --> 01:21:12.499
So, look forward to that.

01:21:12.700 --> 01:21:16.159
On your heart now you ask a question

01:21:16.360 --> 01:21:19.039
because in the heart resides the Spirit.

01:21:19.240 --> 01:21:21.777
So you can address Me as Shri Mataji

01:21:21.944 --> 01:21:25.648
or as Mother, "Mother,

01:21:26.608 --> 01:21:30.471
am I the Spirit?" Ask thrice.

01:21:31.523 --> 01:21:34.400
Without feeling guilty, with full confidence.

01:21:34.601 --> 01:21:38.640
Put the left hand on your lap, parallel to the ground, yes.

01:21:39.360 --> 01:21:41.482
Now, ask a question.

01:21:43.024 --> 01:21:47.749
Left hand parallel does not mean upside down, but open hand,

01:21:47.960 --> 01:21:49.999
open hand, the palm is upward.

01:21:50.200 --> 01:21:52.729
Put the palm upward.

01:21:54.752 --> 01:21:58.905
Now, ask a question, with full confidence.

01:22:25.240 --> 01:22:28.960
Now to know that you are the Spirit

01:22:29.161 --> 01:22:30.926
you have to know one more thing,

01:22:31.127 --> 01:22:33.577
that the Spirit is your Master.

01:22:33.778 --> 01:22:35.640
And once you become the Spirit

01:22:35.841 --> 01:22:38.679
you become your own Master.

01:22:38.880 --> 01:22:43.319
So put your right hand on the left-hand side of your stomach,

01:22:43.520 --> 01:22:47.679
left-hand side of your stomach, in the center, and press it hard

01:22:47.880 --> 01:22:53.690
because that is the place resides the power of your mastery.

01:22:54.192 --> 01:22:56.816
Now, ask a question:

01:22:58.160 --> 01:23:03.800
"Mother, am I my own Master?", "Am I my own Guru?".

01:23:03.960 --> 01:23:05.785
This you have to ask ten times

01:23:05.986 --> 01:23:11.485
because there are ten guru principles within us.

01:24:07.664 --> 01:24:11.942
Now again put the right hand on your heart.

01:24:13.064 --> 01:24:15.479
Now, here, assert yourself

01:24:15.680 --> 01:24:19.400
and say, "Mother, I am the Spirit".

01:24:20.240 --> 01:24:23.960
Say it twelve times, with full assertion and assumption:

01:24:24.160 --> 01:24:27.334
"Mother, I am the Spirit".

01:25:41.800 --> 01:25:46.759
Now, put this right hand on your shoulder

01:25:46.946 --> 01:25:50.119
near your neck, on the left-hand side,

01:25:50.320 --> 01:25:52.840
on your shoulder, near neck.

01:25:53.041 --> 01:25:55.043
This is the place, where I showed you,

01:25:55.244 --> 01:25:57.759
that people, when they feel guilty, there's a catch.

01:25:57.960 --> 01:26:01.247
Press it hard. You'll find it's quite a hard place.

01:26:02.400 --> 01:26:06.418
Here you have to say: "Mother, I am not guilty".

01:26:07.667 --> 01:26:10.239
Say it with full confidence sixteen times.

01:26:10.440 --> 01:26:14.179
And if you have that habit, better say thirty two times.

01:26:19.960 --> 01:26:23.305
Sixteen times, please say, "Mother, I am not guilty".

01:26:23.506 --> 01:26:26.445
You have to forgive yourself.

01:26:39.920 --> 01:26:41.959
You have to forgive yourself

01:26:42.160 --> 01:26:44.880
by saying, "Mother I am not guilty at all, I'm not guilty".

01:26:45.080 --> 01:26:47.960
Put it next to your neck.

01:26:55.832 --> 01:26:58.919
Now, put the right hand

01:26:59.120 --> 01:27:01.502
on the forehead.

01:27:03.680 --> 01:27:07.039
And at this point - across, put it across -

01:27:07.240 --> 01:27:09.532
and now say,

01:27:11.656 --> 01:27:15.109
"Mother, I forgive everyone".

01:27:16.000 --> 01:27:18.039
After forgiving yourself,

01:27:18.240 --> 01:27:21.370
you have to say, "I forgive everyone".

01:27:28.080 --> 01:27:31.749
Across, put your hand across.

01:27:33.703 --> 01:27:37.313
Across, not with your finger but across.

01:27:41.705 --> 01:27:45.359
From your heart you have to say that, "Mother, I forgive everyone".

01:27:45.560 --> 01:27:48.969
You'll feel very much relieved, you just try it.

01:27:50.360 --> 01:27:53.331
Half of your tension will drop away.

01:27:54.640 --> 01:27:58.600
Now, put this hand at the back of your head and hold it tight.

01:27:59.415 --> 01:28:01.399
Hold it tight.

01:28:01.600 --> 01:28:05.537
Now without feeling guilty, without thinking about the past

01:28:05.760 --> 01:28:08.176
in a general way, you have to say

01:28:08.359 --> 01:28:11.152
that, "Oh Lord, oh God,

01:28:11.880 --> 01:28:15.505
if I have done any mistake, please, forgive me".

01:28:17.920 --> 01:28:20.599
Without feeling guilty, that's very important.

01:28:20.800 --> 01:28:24.576
On the back of your head, on the back of your head.

01:28:31.880 --> 01:28:33.815
At the back of your head,

01:28:34.016 --> 01:28:37.029
not on the neck but on the back,

01:28:42.440 --> 01:28:45.732
over the optic lobe, we can say.

01:28:54.407 --> 01:28:57.067
Now put your hand on top of your head,

01:28:57.266 --> 01:28:58.679
in the center of it,

01:28:58.880 --> 01:29:00.680
and press it with your palm,

01:29:00.880 --> 01:29:03.880
and try to move it clockwise.

01:29:14.000 --> 01:29:16.667
Move it clockwise.

01:29:19.160 --> 01:29:22.520
At this point as I said I cannot cross your freedom.

01:29:22.726 --> 01:29:24.991
Keep it in a comfortable way.

01:29:25.599 --> 01:29:27.648
Comfortable way. From the front if you put it,

01:29:27.815 --> 01:29:29.599
it will be comfortable.

01:29:29.800 --> 01:29:31.719
And move it a little bit.

01:29:31.920 --> 01:29:35.589
And now, at this point, as I cannot cross your freedom

01:29:35.790 --> 01:29:40.283
you have to say: "Mother, please give me my Realization".

01:29:42.236 --> 01:29:44.800
Because I cannot do it without your permission.

01:29:45.000 --> 01:29:48.199
"I want my Realization. Please, give me Realization".

01:29:48.400 --> 01:29:50.870
Just ask for it.

01:29:56.080 --> 01:29:58.255
Seven times.

01:30:22.720 --> 01:30:24.879
Now put your hand down

01:30:25.080 --> 01:30:27.679
and with your left hand,

01:30:27.880 --> 01:30:30.519
feel if there's a cool breeze coming,

01:30:30.720 --> 01:30:33.362
on top of your head.

01:30:43.735 --> 01:30:45.742
Raise it higher to see

01:30:45.943 --> 01:30:49.699
not very high, but at a higher point. Because close to your head

01:30:49.900 --> 01:30:52.719
you might feel the heat coming out of your head.

01:30:52.920 --> 01:30:56.605
So little higher, not much, about six inches.

01:31:01.040 --> 01:31:04.236
See now, if there's cool breeze coming.

01:31:09.400 --> 01:31:13.253
Don't think about it. If you think about it, it will stop.

01:31:14.720 --> 01:31:16.346
Now change your hand if you want.

01:31:16.547 --> 01:31:18.439
Again see with your right hand.

01:31:18.640 --> 01:31:22.000
Just see, if there is a cool breeze coming here.

01:31:51.944 --> 01:31:55.071
Are you feeling the cool breeze?

01:32:02.000 --> 01:32:04.280
Now I'll teach you how to raise your own Kundalini.

01:32:04.481 --> 01:32:05.858
You can open your eyes.

01:32:06.059 --> 01:32:09.200
Now do it without thinking, try to see Me without thinking.

01:32:09.401 --> 01:32:11.360
You have to do it. Don't think about it.

01:32:11.560 --> 01:32:14.680
It's just an action of your hand because it is awakened now.

01:32:14.881 --> 01:32:16.299
So we have to establish it.

01:32:16.339 --> 01:32:19.399
Just put this left hand in front - by sitting only -

01:32:19.600 --> 01:32:23.117
in front of your Kundalini, like this.

01:32:23.680 --> 01:32:25.618
Like this.

01:32:26.120 --> 01:32:29.439
Can you see? Just like this, while you're sitting. Left hand.

01:32:29.640 --> 01:32:32.160
Now, with the right hand you have to move it like this,

01:32:32.361 --> 01:32:34.635
forward, downward, backward, upward.

01:32:34.836 --> 01:32:36.360
Like that, you see? Like this.

01:32:36.561 --> 01:32:40.159
Now, let us start. We have to go up.

01:32:45.200 --> 01:32:49.159
Take it up, through your head up and

01:32:49.360 --> 01:32:53.325
twist it now and give it a knot.

01:32:53.547 --> 01:32:55.380
Again, let's try.

01:32:55.581 --> 01:32:57.360
Once more.
